Dataset Presentation¶

Source : ISIC 2016 challenge¶

https://challenge.isic-archive.com/landing/2016/

  • Part 1 : Skin lesion segmentation
  • Part 2 : Skin lesion classification

The dataset contains 900 skin lesion images (726 benign, 174 malignant) with ground truth masks annotations.

In [61]:
fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 4, figsize=(15,5))

for i in range(4):
    im = plt.imread(imgs[i])
    axs[i].imshow(im)
    axs[i].axis('off')
fig.suptitle("Skin lesion masks", fontsize=20, y=0.87)
plt.show()
